SUMMARY:Mayors Food Truck Fiesta
LOCATION:241-\, 263 E Madison St Tampa \, FL 33602 United States
DESCRIPTION:Lets fiesta! Back by popular demand (and hunger)\, the Mayors 
 Food Truck Fiesta is rolling in to Lykes Gaslight Park the first Wednesday
  of every month from 11am to 2pm. Join us for truckloads of local favorite
 s and food that goes the extra mile. (Literally!) Thank you to the City of
  Tampa for their sponsorship of this event. (Interested in becoming a vend
 or? Contact Tampa Downtown Partnership!) - - - - - - - - - - Vmonos de fie
 sta! Debido a su popularidad (y hambre)\, el Mayors Food Truck Fiesta va a
  hacer una parada en el parque de Lykes Gaslight el primer mircoles de cad
 a mes desde las 11am a las 2pm. Acompanos y disfruta de los mejores sabore
 s sobre ruedas de la ciudad. Gracias a la Ciudad de Tampa por patrocinar e
 l evento. (Tienes un food truck y quieres participar en el evento? Contact
 a a Tampa Downtown Partnership!) \n\nPermalink: https://www.tampa.gov/node
 /179626
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.tampa.gov/node/179626
END:VEVENT
